description:
With Clever’s app you always close to your next charge on Denmark’s largest charging network.

In the app you can:

- Find next available Clever charging station
- Start and stop charging on Clever charging stations + other selected charging networks
- Pay for charging with Apple Pay and credit card
- Search for standard, fast and ultra-fast charging stations (11-300 kW)
- Filter the charging station map by plug types your car uses, - and follow the charging points you use regularly
- Navigate to your chosen charging station with Google Maps
- Get step-by-step instructions when using a charging station, you’re not familiar with

If you are a Clever customer, you can furthermore:

- Follow your home and away consumption
- Use a digital copy of your Clever charge key
- Quick start charging on Clever’s charge network
- Activate and control intelligent charging on your home Clever charging device

Slut dig til vores 300.000 brugere, som allerede bruger OK-appen til at tanke, vaske, parkere og oplade bilen i hele Danmark.

Uanset om du vil betale med MobilePay, Apple Pay, Dankort, Visa/MasterCard eller dit OK Kort, har du altid betalingen lige ved hånden med OK-appen.

TANK I NÆRHEDEN

Åbn standeren og betal for din tankning i OK-appen eller med Apple CarPlay. Du får en kvittering efter hver tankning, som bliver gemt direkte i appen. Du kan altid finde den nærmeste OK-tankstation og selv vælge, hvilken klub eller forening du vil støtte, når du tanker benzin og diesel.

BILVASK

Det har aldrig været nemmere at have en ren bil. Start vasken direkte i appen, og bliv siddende i bilen, mens den bliver vasket. Uanset om du køber en enkelt vask eller har vores OK Fri Vask-abonnement, er det hurtigt og ligetil.

PARKERING

Med OK’s app kan du finde parkeringspladser i nærheden og nemt starte, forlænge og afslutte din parkering. Når du først har tilføjet din nummerplade i appen og valgt betalingsmiddel, er det lige til at komme i gang. Du kan også parkere med Apple CarPlay.

Det bedste er, at du kan klare det hele fra dit forsæde eller på caféen, hvis du lige får lyst til en ekstra muffin til caffé latten – så slipper du for at stå i kø til parkeringsautomaten. Vi giver dig også gerne en påmindelse, hvis din parkering er ved at udløbe.

Som Coop-medlem optjener du også bonus fra Coop, når du parkerer med appen. Tilknyt dit Coop-medlemsnummer til OK-appen, så kommer din bonus fra Coop automatisk ind på din medlemskonto.

Derudover kan du også tilføje noter til dine kvitteringer og gratis sende din kvittering til din e-mail.

Du kan parkere med OK-appen i København, Frederiksberg, Aarhus, Aalborg, Odense, Vejle, Skagen og mange andre byer i hele landet.

OPLADNING

Når du er på farten, kan OK's app navigere dig til en ledig OK-ladestander. I appen kan du se hastighed, priser og stiktyper samt starte, stoppe og betale en opladning.

Med en ladeboks fra OK kan du se elprisen og udskyde din opladning til det billigste tidspunkt. Du kan også følge med i dit forbrug for din elbil og plugin hybrid i appen.

Sæt bare stikket i bilen og start opladningen – så klarer vi resten.

Norlys Charging is tailored to make your charging experience as pleasant and simple as possible.

When charging at home, all you need to do is plug in the car, and then leave the rest to us. The app ensures that your car charges in the cheapest, greenest, or most sustainable way - depending on your preference.

You can set your SmartCharge to prioritize green energy, save costs, or reduce CO2 emissions. Just set your preferences; Norlys Charging takes care of the rest.

After you're done charging, you can get a detailed overview of your charging sessions, including costs and usage patterns, which helps provide a better insight for future charging.

When you're on the go, the app makes it easy to find charging stations, view charging prices and speeds, get an overview of availability, and of course, start charging. With the app, you can always find Norlys public charging points, as well as roaming charging points – did you know there are over 500,000 charging points across Europe? 

You choose how you want to pay - via Apple Pay, MobilePay, or credit card. You can also choose "Pay with Norlys," where charges are paid through your monthly electricity bill - easy and convenient.

You can read more and order a charging solution for your home at norlys.dk/charging.

Explore and navigate the world with confidence using Google Maps. Find the best routes with live traffic data and real-time GPS navigation for driving, walking, cycling and public transport. Discover over 250 million businesses and places – from restaurants and shops to everyday essentials – with photos, reviews and helpful information.

Navigate the world, the way that you want:
• Get to where you need to go with fuel-efficient route options
• Find the best route with real-time, turn-by-turn voice and on-screen navigation
• Save time with automatic rerouting based on live traffic, incidents and road closures
• Catch the bus, train and ride-share effortlessly, with real-time updates
• Find bike or scooter rentals to get around more easily

Plan trips and experiences effortlessly:
• Preview an area before you go (e.g. parking, entrances) with Street View
• Use Immersive View to experience what landmarks, parks and routes look like, and even check the weather so that you can be ready in advance
• Create custom lists of your favourite saved places and share with others
• Order delivery and takeaway, make reservations and book hotels
• Don't get lost with offline maps in an area with bad signal
• Search for local places and things to do, and decide based on user reviews and photos

Discover and explore like a local:
• Explore with confidence knowing 500 million users contribute and keep the map up to date each year
• Avoid the crowds by seeing how busy a place is before you get there
• Use Lens in Maps to see walking directions overlaid on the real world
• Filter restaurants by cuisine, hours, price, rating and more
• Ask questions about a place, from dishes to parking, and get quick answers

Some features not available in all countries or cities
Navigation isn't intended to be used by oversized or emergency vehicles

The Circle K Charge app is easy to use, gives you a great overview and access to practical functions when charging in Sweden, Norway, Denmark or Estonia

Find our stations  
The charger map makes it easy for you to find the nearest station, charging stations along your route or an overview of available chargers so you don’t have to spend more time than necessary on planning your trip.

Full overview 
Using the app when charging gives you the full overview of your charging session. You will easily see the battery status, charging speed and progress on your phone.

Boundless charging 
The Charge app can be used all over Scandinavia. You will therefore have the same charging experience in all countries - no matter where you are.

Charging history  
You will be able to find an overview of your charging history in the app menu. This makes it easy to find previous charging stops, pricing, charging time and average speed.

Kør trygt. Spar penge. Undgå ulykker.

Hent Saphe Link-appen og få præcise advarsler om fartkontroller, ulykker og farer på vejene – så du kan fokusere på at komme sikkert frem.
 
Derfor bruger flere millioner bilister Saphe:
Alarmer om fartkontroller, ulykker og andre farer – i hele Europa.
Starter automatisk, når du starter bilen.
Nem og sikker betjening med tydelig visning af hændelser og afstand dertil på trafikalarmens skærm.
En del af et internationalt trafikfællesskab med over 11 millioner brugere, der hjælper hinanden i trafikken.
Saphe T — vores bedste trafikalarm til dato
Saphe T er næste generation af Saphe-enheder med forbedret skærm og længere batterilevetid. Den bygger videre på Saphe Drive Pro og Mini og gør det endnu nemmere at køre trygt.
 
Ekstra funktioner med Saphe Premium eller Premium+:
Se aktuelle og kommende hastighedsgrænser.
Bliv advaret, hvis du kører for stærkt.
Se din præcise hastighed, direkte på din Saphe.
Forbind til Apple Carplay.
Med et Saphe abonnement er du altid opdateret med de nyeste funktioner – og et aktivt abonnement er påkrævet til Saphe Drive Mini, Pro og T. Premium kan også bruges sammen med Saphe One, One+ og Drive.
 
Sådan kommer du i gang:
Download Saphe Link-appen.
Opret din brugerkonto.
Forbind din Saphe-enhed i Saphe Link-appen.
Aktivér/opret et Saphe abonnement (påkrævet til Saphe T, Pro og Mini).
Placer trafikalarmen i bilen inden for syns- og rækkevidde – og kør trygt afsted.

Læs mere på www.saphe.com

Connect, charge and go!  
The Spirii Go app offers effortless EV charging across Europe and at home. Our streamlined app packs in smart navigation, Europe-wide roaming, multiple payment options, and customisable home charging tools – giving you full flexibility and unrivalled convenience.

Access a European-wide charging network
Spirii Go is fully integrated with Europe’s most preferred roaming platform, allowing seamless access to charging points no matter where your journey takes you.

Tailor-made charging
Easily filter all charging stations by available plug-types, charging speed and operators.

Hassle-free payment
With smart settings and multiple payment methods, you can charge and pay without worry – and with full control over your usage and finances.

Get a full overview 
Access up-to-date charging prices, availability, and opening hours for any charging station, and track your spending across weeks, months, or years.

Smooth navigation
Find your nearest or preferred chargers and follow turn-by-turn directions with Google Maps, Apple Maps, or a range of other popular mapping options.

Charge smarter and greener with detailed energy insights
Explore real-time energy insights in the app and schedule charging for times when electricity prices are at their lowest and climate impact minimised

Trusted customer support 24/7
Problems with the app or charging? Don’t hesitate to contact us! We are available 24/7 and we are doing our best. In fact, our customers rate us 4.5 at Trustpilot.

Med GET LIT kan du oplade din telefon frit i byen uden det skal være besværligt.


De smarte powerbanks har indbygget 3 forskellige stik, der passer til de fleste telefoner - også earpods og andre trådløse enheder. (microUSB, USB-C og Lightning kabler)


Fuld frihed så du ikke behøver at vente ved en stikkontakt eller have egen ledning med.


Vi har teamet op med restauratører og barer i hele Danmark, så GET LIT altid kan findes i din by.


Hvordan det virker:

1.    Scan QR kode på ladeboksen for at udløse din powerbank  

3.   Tag din powerbank og oplad på stedet eller ta' den med dig til næste lokation

4.   Powerbanken kan returneres i alle GET LITs  lokationer i hele Danmark. 


Super simpelt og hurtigt


Priser:

20 kr. / time.

75 kr. / 24 timer


For mere information besøg os på: www.get-lit.dk

Stay in control of your EV charging experience—at home and on the go. No monthly subscription, 100% free. Winner of best EV app/software at E-Mobility Awards 2023.

Monta Charge is the digital companion for any EV lifestyle, which makes owning an electric vehicle an exciting and hassle-free ride. Whether at home or on the road, we cover all the bases, ensuring you have complete control of your charging experience. With Monta, you just need one app for all your charging needs, no matter where your journey takes you.
New to the EV lifestyle or an EV pro? Either way, you're in good hands with us. We’re here to make sure your charging experience is as seamless and convenient as possible. Just sit back and enjoy your EV; we'll take care of the rest.

Your home, your charger, your rules
An effortless EV experience starts right at home. With Monta Charge, you have the power to customise your charging settings to match your lifestyle and enjoy set-and-forget charging.
- Choose between 400 charger models that fits your needs and budget best
- Own and manage up to 3 charge points at multiple locations
- Share your charger with family, friends, and neighbours and set rules for when and who can access it
- Charge greener and cheaper: schedule charges to automatically start when electricity prices and CO2 emissions are at their lowest
- Integrate your car with Monta to see your car’s current battery level, whether the cable is plugged in, or if your car is currently charging
- Track your EV's charge history, monitor its performance, and gain insights into your energy spending and usage patterns

Your digital companion for seamless EV charging anywhere
Heading to work, running errands, or going on a road trip? Monta Charge keeps you in the driver’s seat at all times. Hit the road without hesitation, knowing you’re covered by a vast network of accessible charge points, transparent pricing, and flexible payment options.
- Quickly locate any of the 650,000+ supported public chargers on the Monta map and easily get directions with Google Maps and Apple Maps
- Filter charge points by availability, charge speed (kW), price (dynamic or fixed pricing), operator, and more
- No hidden fees, always see what you’ll pay for upfront: the price breakdown, our cut, and who sets the price
- Scan the QR code on a charger to charge your EV without registration if you’re in a hurry
- Connect to a charger via the Monta Charge app or by tapping an RFID card on the charger;
- Add funds to your Monta Wallet or simply pay via credit card, Apple Pay, Google Pay, or MobilePay/Vipps (Nordics)
- View all your transactions in one place and keep track of your charging history
- Easily export any receipts and invoices and never worry about misplaced receipts again

There for you 24/7
Looking for some help or have any questions? Don't worry, our amazing support team is just a message away, always ready to assist you whenever you need it.

Join the thriving community of over 200,000 EV enthusiasts who have seamlessly adopted the EV lifestyle with our award-winning Monta Charge app!

Welcome to E.ON Drive Comfort

Take us with you on your journeys, no matter where you start. Wherever you go,
we'll find the right charging station for you. Plan less and drive more.
Download the E.ON Drive Comfort app now and become part of the E.ON Drive
community.

__ Relaxed charging – thanks to intelligent recommendations and real-time
ratings
With smart recommendations and a real-time rating system, you’ll find the most
reliable charging points near you. Additionally, we offer many other features to
make your charging experience seamless.

__ Easily find what you're looking for – with the "Amenities" feature
We don’t just show you if a charging station is open and whether a spot is
available. With E.ON Drive Comfort, you’ll also find the charging point that
meets your needs. Whether it's a station with a roof to protect you from rain or
a rest area with a toilet for a quick stop, we’ve got you covered. We also provide
images of the station, so you’ll know exactly what to expect.

__ Transparent pricing and tariffs for everyone
Whether you use public charging stations regularly or only occasionally: Simply
choose the tariff that suits you. Our kWh-based billing tariffs with monthly
cancellation options and fixed prices offer maximum flexibility. You can choose
between E.ON Drive Flex with no basic fee for occasional charging or E.ON
Drive Plus with discounted kWh prices for regular charging. Just pick the right
tariff and charge at more than 500,000 charging points across Europe.

__ We make e-mobility easier – are you in?
Is something missing? Let us know! We are continuously developing E.ON Drive
Comfort, and we want to do it together with you to make e-mobility even easier.
We’re always happy to receive your ideas and suggestions for improvement.

With the Q8 app, we’ve made it easy and convenient for you to fuel and wash your car – while also enjoying great deals with our coupons when you visit our stations. Add your Q8 card or Dankort, Visa or Mastercard, and you're ready to fuel or wash. We also store your receipts in the app. 

You can find the station closest to you, see information about opening hours, and what the station offers. 

With our app in hand, you can: 

• Pay for fueling at Q8 and F24 stations 
• Get access to great deals and benefits with our coupons. 
• Purchase car wash subscriptions and single washes, and wash your car without having to get out of the car 
• Find the nearest station
• Find your receipts 

And if you have something on your mind or want to share, you can also find our customer service contact information. 

Enjoy!

Med Q8 er du altid tæt på en lader til din bil. Du får tilgang til alle ladestandere i Q8s netværk, som giver dig friheden til at køre derhen du ønsker. Alt du skal gøre, er at tilslutte bilen og igangsætte opladningen, så håndterer vi resten. 
Appen hjælper dig frem til en ledig lader, hvor du vil kunne:

•	Se kort over ladestandere samt mulighed for at se tilgængelighed
•	Betale med dit betalingskort
•	Starte og afslutte din opladning
•	Overvåge opladningen på distance
•	Opkoble din hjemmelader og få en samlet ladestatistik
•	Filtrere kortet over ladestandere på almindelige-, hurtige- og lynladere
•	Filtrere på kortet over ladestandere efter stiktype, der passer til din bil

Udover Q8s netværk får du adgang til ladestationer i hele Europa via vores roamingpartnere. For at kunne udnytte app’ens fulde funktionalitet skal du registrere dig i appen eller på registrering.q8.dk

Du vil en gang om måneden blive debiteret for din opladning, fra det betalingskort du ønsker at tilknytte.
Debiteringen håndteres af vores samarbejdspartner Virta.

God rejse.

Say hi to your co-driver.

You’re searching for a top-notch EV charging experience? Here you are: Download the IONITY App to access Europe’s leading High-Power Charging (HPC) network available across 24 countries – open to EVs from all manufacturers. Our network delivers maximum charging speeds of up to 400 kW, enabling you to charge 300 kilometres of range in 15 minutes. Faster charging sessions — more time for you. 

Discover the highlights of the IONITY App

Navigation
•	Search and find the nearest or a specific IONITY Station — the availability of all charging points is displayed in real-time.
•	Use the IONITY Route Planner to plan your journey ahead and import your daily or upcoming routes to your favourite navigation app with ease. 

Charging
•	Conveniently start and end your charging session directly within the IONITY App.
•	Track your charging progress in real-time and receive a push notification when you’re at 80% to go back on the road.
•	Optional: Use our app to scan the QR code on the charger to start the session. 

Payment
•	Safely store your account and payment details within the app to conveniently pay for your charging sessions.
•	Receive monthly invoices for your personal or professional use to keep an eye on your spendings.
•	Have a closer look at your past IONITY charging sessions and explore useful information like session duration, kWh charged and charging curves.

Find the right IONITY Subscription for you

Discover our subscriptions within the app: Choose the one that matches your lifestyle, driving habits, and charging needs by opting for IONITY Power or Motion. Sign up now and charge your electric vehicle at very attractive price per kWh. Prices vary by country. 

IONITY Power
Power your EV and charge for less: Our IONITY Power subscription is the right choice for most EV drivers. You save money after only two charging sessions per month: Benefit from the cheapest charging prices per kWh and continue your journey fast.

IONITY Motion
Keep yourself in motion: IONITY Motion is the ideal subscription for drivers that only occasionally use their electric vehicle and want to benefit from a cheaper charging price per kWh by using the IONITY App.

Your benefits with IONITY Power and IONITY Motion:
•	A significantly lower charging price per kWh
•	No seasonal or peak changes of kWh prices
•	Switch your current subscription anytime 
•	Cancel subscription anytime to next billing date
•	Subscribe and pay via the IONITY App

Charging for registered users without IONITY Power or Motion subscription:

IONITY Go
Ready. Set. Go! Sign up within the IONITY App and automatically benefit from a slightly lower charging price per kWh. No subscription and no monthly fees. This is IONITY Go. Upgrade to our subscriptions to save even more.

About IONITY
IONITY builds and operates Europe’s largest ultra-fast charging network. With a High-Power Charging (HPC) capacity of up to 400 kW, it enables maximum charging speeds. IONITY exclusively uses renewable energy, ensuring emission-free and carbon-neutral driving. Currently, the IONITY network includes over 700 charging stations and more than 4,800 HPC charging points across 24 European countries.

IONITY was founded in 2017 and is a joint venture between the car manufacturers BMW Group, Ford Motor Company, Hyundai Motor Group, Kia, Mercedes-Benz AG and Volkswagen Group with Audi and Porsche as well as BlackRock's Climate Infrastructure Platform as a financial investor. The company is headquartered in Munich, Germany, and has additional offices in Dortmund, Germany, the French metropolis Paris, and outside the Norwegian capital Oslo. Further information at www.ionity.eu.

A Better Routeplanner (ABRP) is the world's most respected service to plan, learn and dream about Electric Vehicles - EVs. Simply select your vehicle model, enter your destination and hit plan to get a full trip plan including charge stops and trip duration.
When you are ready to drive it, just go to driving mode and use ABRP as a real-time plan follow-up tool and even navigator, replan as necessary and get continuously updated information about your trip.
We support every major EV in the market. Which suits your needs best?

Find charging stations and get information about charging speed, current prices and availability in real time. Live charger status is displayed for all major networks in Scandinavia and several in rest of Europe. In one place you can now see if a charger is idle, busy or out of order regardless of operator. Tips on nearby eateries and other things that can be good to know about the specific place are of course also available.

On the map, it is easy to get a quick overview of which chargers are available. Different colors of map pins show charging speed and with the map filter it is easy to customize the type of charger you want to see.

The route planner is a tool for finding fast chargers along a specific route. Enter your criteria for the route and ChargeFinder calculates an optimal route, shows distances to the stations, indicates the length of the detour and presents everything in a clear format.

Île-de-France Mobilités is here to assist you daily. Purchase a digital ticket, recharge your Navigo pass, search for routes including trains, RERs, metros, trams, buses, coaches, bicycles, Vélib', car-sharing, or car rentals. Find schedules in real-time or traffic information... Discover essential tools and information for organizing your travels in Île-de-France. Together, let's travel with ease.

Avoid queues at stations: buy your transport tickets from your iPhone!
The following tickets are available for purchase:

- Metro-Train tickets or Bus-Tram Ticket
- One Way from/to Airports (you cannot purchase this ticket if you already have a Metro-Train Ticket charged on your device)
- Navigo daily (this fare doesn’t permit you to go to airports), weekly, or monthly passes
- Special fares (Anti-pollution pass, Paris-Visit Passes etc.)
- Daily Vélib’ passes

Purchased tickets can then be (depending on the chosen purchasing path):

- Stored on the iPhone and validated directly at stations (from iPhone Xr and iOS 17.5)
- Loaded onto your Navigo pass (from an iPhone 7, with at least iOS 13. iPhone XR and XS are compatible starting from iOS 14.5)

For compatible tickets (Metro-Train and Bus-Tram Tickets, Navigo Day passes, special fares), no account is needed, and you can pay directly with Apple Pay!

You can prepare and plan your travels:

- Find nearby bus stops, train stations, and metro stations
- Search for real-time public transport routes, car-sharing, and bicycle routes
- Save upcoming trips in your phone’s calendar
- Check the next departures for your lines in real-time and all the timetable information
- View maps of public transport networks (accessible even offline)
- Follow pedestrian routes for walking segment

Stay informed and anticipate disruptions:

- Check your lines’ Twitter feed for real-time traffic updates
- Get alerts for disruptions on your favorite lines and routes
- Stay updated on the status of elevators in the stations you use

Customize your travel:

- Save your destinations (work, home, gym, etc.), stations, and stops as favorites
- Customize your profile (fast walker, with difficulties, reduced mobility, etc.)
- Select lines or stations to avoid

Prefer soft or alternative modes of transport:

- Book car-sharing and/or ride-sharing trips in partnership with leading providers
- Opt for bicycle routes for all your trips
- Rent a car or a van for a short period by choosing a Communauto car-sharing vehicle from a wide selection of stations around you and book it immediately for the duration of your choice.
--
Already using the Île-de-France Mobilités app and enjoying its services? Let us know with a 5-star rating!
Experiencing bugs or having feedback to give? Help us improve by sending your suggestions through the contact form available via the personal space.

We're with you for the journey – wherever and whenever you need to recharge.

Key features:

Med Uno-X Opladnings Appen får du adgang til alle Uno-X lynladere og over 5.000 øvrige ladepunkter i hele Danmark. Uanset hvor du er på vej, gør app'en det let at finde nærmeste ladestander, der passer til dit behov.

- Finde ledige Uno-X Lynladere samt ladepunkter fra andre operatører i nærheden af dig

Det er nemt at komme i gang. Download appen, opret en konto eller log ind, og find ladestandere i nærheden.

Moovit is one app for all your urban mobility and transport rides!

Dailymail - "This travel app is a godsend for anyone using public transport – with live updates to bus schedules, as well as a great route-planner for cities across the UK."

Transportation is an integral part of urban living. Whether you ride the train, subway/underground /tube, bus, light rail, ferry or metro, use bikes, ride-sharing like Uber, getting the best urban mobility information is critical. Moovit guides you from point A to B in the easiest and most efficient way. Get train and bus times, maps, and live arrival times with ease so you can plan your trip with confidence. Find critical alerts and service disruptions for your favorite lines. Get step-by-step directions of optimal route bus, train, metro, bike or a combination of them. 
This is why Moovit has been named one of the best apps of the year 2017 by the App Store!

Moovit guides more than 865 million users in over 3200 cities throughout the world.

► Journey Planner that combines you all transport options and gives you the best route with live arrivals.

► Live Directions: Get step-by-step directions with live guidance as you travel: know exactly how long you need to walk to your station, how long you’re waiting, view the arrival time of your line and how many stops are left. 

► Real time arrivals. View real-time arrival updates, which are taken directly from GPS devices positioned on buses and trains.

► Real time alerts. Know about issues ahead of time by receiving service alerts such as emergency or unexpected disruptions, delays, traffic jams, new construction and more...

► Users reports. Moovit’s users report issues found with stations, line service, and timetables so that we can inform all nearby riders about what’s going on in their area.

► Favorite lines, stations, and places. Get easy access to lines, stations, and places you ride and visit all the time. Plus, get real-time updates if/when there are changes to your favorite lines in case your bus or train time is impacted!

► Bike routes. Get bike routes in addition to the bus, subway, train, or metro trip plans. If you ride bikes (yours or shared) we can plan a route that includes the train or bus.

Know what's ahead on the road with the help from other drivers. Waze is a live map that harnesses the local knowledge of tens of millions of drivers around the world. Drivers safely and confidently reach their everyday destinations thanks to Waze map’s GPS navigation, live traffic updates, real-time safety alerts (including roadworks, accidents, crashes, police, potholes and more) and accurate ETAs.


Make your next drive more predictable and stress-free:
• Get there faster with real-time directions, accurate ETAs and automatic rerouting based on live traffic, incidents and road closures
• Even if you know the way, avoid surprises on the road ahead with safety alerts for accidents, crashes, roadworks, objects on the road, potholes, speed bumps, sharp curves, bad weather, emergency vehicles, railway crossings and more
• Steer clear of tickets by knowing where police and red light and speed cameras are located
• Share what’s happening on the road with other drivers by reporting live incidents and hazards
• Stay informed of upcoming speed limit changes, and keep your speedometer in check
• Know which lane to be in with multi-lane guidance
• See toll pricing and choose to avoid tolls along your routes
• Add road passes and vignettes for HOV lanes and restricted traffic zones
• Find petrol/fuel stations and prices and EV charging stations along your route
• Locate car parks near your destination
• Use voice-guided turn-by-turn navigation from a variety of languages, local accents and your favourite celebrities
• Plan your next drive by checking ETAs by future departure or arrival times
• Use your favourite audio apps (for podcasts, music, news, audiobooks) directly within Waze
• Sync Waze to your car’s built-in display through Apple CarPlay


* Some features are not available in all countries


* Waze navigation is not intended for emergency or oversized vehicles


You can manage your in-app Waze privacy settings at any time. Learn more about the Waze privacy policy here, www.waze.com/legal/privacy.

Travel confidently around London with Transport for London's official app, built around our iconic live Tube map. Try switching to step-free mode and watch the map adjust to show only accessible stations, ensuring your journeys are as smooth as possible. With a clear, user-friendly design, TfL Go is easy for everyone to use.

Find the Best Route
We'll suggest multiple ways to get to your destination, whether by Tube, London Overground, Elizabeth line, DLR, Tram, National Rail, IFS Cloud Cable Car, or even cycling and walking. You choose the route that suits you best.

Check Before You Travel
Get live arrival times for Buses, Tube, London Overground, Elizabeth Line, DLR, Tram, and National Rail. Check the live status of all TfL lines and stations directly on the map, or view a summary of current disruptions in the "Status" section.

Freedom to Explore
Find travel options tailored to your needs, including step-free journeys and routes avoiding stairs or escalators. Journey plans automatically adapt to the accessibility status of stations, helping you avoid disruptions. TfL Go also supports VoiceOver and Dynamic Type, making it more accessible for everyone.

Manage Your Payments
Create an account or log in to manage your payments for travel across London. Top up pay as you go credit or purchase Travelcards for your Oyster card, and view your journey history for both Oyster and contactless cards registered to your account.

Note: Oyster and contactless accounts can only be accessed within UK/Europe.

Understand Station Facilities
Check how busy a station is right now, or see if it has toilets or Wi-Fi access. Find detailed information about step-free access and interchanges including platform gap width, step height and boarding methods available.

Med EWII Opladning appen får du nemt fyldt batteriet op på din elbil. Spar penge, brug grøn energi eller lad bilen op, når CO2-udledningen er lavest. Du skal bare indstille dine SmartCharge-præferencer én gang, så sørger EWII Opladning for resten.  Appen giver dig overblik over dit forbrug og omkostningen ved hver enkelt ladning.

EWII Opladning er designet til at hjælpe dig med at lade bedre, uanset om du er hjemme, på arbejdet eller på farten. Du kan lade på over 500.000 offentlige ladestandere fordelt i Danmark og resten af Europa. Med appen kan du nemt se ladepriser og hastigheder og finde ledige ladestandere. Og selve opladningen starter du nemt direkte fra appen.

Med en serviceaftale hos EWII får du automatisk udbetalt elrefusion af dit elforbrug på opladning. Det sker direkte i din wallet på telefonen efter hver opladning (det gælder ikke for kunder med solceller eller elvarme).

Læs mere og bestil din ladeløsning på: ewii.dk/ladeboks

ParkZone Go giver enkel og hurtig adgang til din ParkCare-bruger. Du får en nem løsning, der både virker på mobil og tablet, så du altid har mulighed for at registrere din bil med få klik. Du opretter registreringerne på samme måde, som du plejer at gøre via din computer. Du kan også se dine tidligere registreringer, rette i de igangværende, eller slette hvis du får en ny bil.

ParkZone Go inkluderer desuden en betalingsfunktion, der kan anvendes på ParkZones egne pladser. Via kortet kan du se hvilke parkeringsområder, der er nær dig. Du skal blot vælge et parkeringsområde, indtaste dit køretøjs registreringsnummer og vælge den ønskede betalingsmåde. Du kan starte, stoppe og forlænge din parkering med få klik, eller benytte dig af forudbetalt parkering. Hvad enten mødet trækker ud, eller du har brug for mere shoppetid, kan din parkering nemt og hurtigt administreres via ParkZone Go.

Du kan benytte ParkZone Gos betalingsfunktion i København, Helsingør, Køge, Frederiksberg, Odense, Vejle, Aarhus, Aalborg, Frederikshavn og mange andre byer rundt omkring i Danmark.
